    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. From the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously cared for, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants the very best.",
